{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 129840, "create_time": 1653105322, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "patpat", "timestamp": 1653105322}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 129845, "create_time": 1653105525, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "之前也相信真的大家都很辛苦，后来发现他们说的辛苦和我好像很不一样。轻描淡写地安慰我说大家都很累，可能是没有经历过绝望无力的感觉吧，人类的悲欢不可能相通……", "timestamp": 1653105525}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 129865, "create_time": 1653106198, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/45723074/answer/137448992", "timestamp": 1653106198}], "create_time": 1653101333, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1653106198, "likenum": 3, "n_attentions": 3, "n_comments": 3, "pid": 45340, "poll": null, "reply": 3, "text": "我是日常情绪不稳型，焦虑、抑郁、低落、紧张，轮番来袭。很长一段时间内，我都以为世界上的人大抵如此，只不过大家都伪装得很好罢了，谁不是这么辛苦呢？但是活到现在，我突然发现，大部分人都不是这样的，他们真心地享受生活，没有那么多小情绪大情绪，睡得香吃得香，哭笑自如。像我这样心里迷雾重重，哭不出也笑不出的人，其实是少数。", "timestamp": 1653101333}}